HEADWORD: Pesade
<hw>Pe*sade"</hw> <pr>(p⟦esl⟧*s⟦amac⟧d"; F. p⟦eit⟧*z⟦adot⟧d")</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety> <fld>(Man.)</fld> <def>The motion of a
